message.entry: The simulation of the model ''{0}'' was terminated because the specified stop time {1} is less than or equal to the snapshot time stored in the initial ModelOperatingPoint. Specify a stop time which is greater than the snapshot time {2} to continue the simulation.
Saving or restoring the operating point for model ''{0}'' is not supported in rapid accelerator simulation mode due to multiple reasons.

To avoid this behavior, explicitly specify the solver max step size before saving model operating point.
